*Nositi* ga je bilo teško. (It was hard to carry him.)
Ona voli da *nosi* dugu kosu. (She likes to wear long hair.)
Imao je odgovornost da *nosi* svoje brige. (He had the responsibility to carry his worries.)
Ona je imala običaj da *nosi* crvene cipele. (She had a habit of wearing red shoes.)
Deca su se takmičila u tome ko će *nositi* najviše kesa. (The children competed to carry the most bags.)
On je nosio *noseći* korpu. (He was carrying a basket.)
Pola sata je proveo *noseći* teške kofere. (He spent half an hour carrying heavy suitcases.)